title: Friday Feast with PA and Charch!
description: Oklahoma co-OC/OL coach Bill Bedenbaugh offered Dru Samia intel, Kevin Gorg & Brian Arrigoni in studio to break down the Derby and NHL Playoffs, then Chad Greenway hung out in studio for most of the final hour!!
